refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
intshmop_size Shmopshmop
shmop_size is used to get the size, in bytes of the shared memory block.

&reftitle.parameters;
shmop
The shared memory block identifier created by shmop_open

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns an int, which represents the number of bytes the shared memory
 block occupies.

